The nurse, feeling spurned and neglected, plays a cruel prank on TomÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¡s, altering blood test results to suggest that he is H.I.V.-positive. This leads to some anguished soul-searching and also, rather improbably, to a madcap chase that ends on the observation deck of the Latin American Tower, Mexico CityÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã¢â€žÂ¢s answer to the Empire State Building.

